  "detailed_description": "Ready to die? Experience the newest brutal action game from Team NINJA and Koei Tecmo Games. In the age of samurai, a lone traveler lands on the shores of Japan. He must fight his way through the vicious warriors and supernatural Yokai that infest the land in order to find that which he seeks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/ab0961e37bba777ec859c3e8368c1e33.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/7c4edb97087cb46b1fb839a98daaf956.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br> The Complete Edition contains the full game, as well as the three expansions with additional story chapters: Dragon of the North, Defiant Honor, and Bloodshed's End.<br><br>Dragon of the North<br>This expansion opens up the Tohoku region, where the \"one-eyed dragon\" Date Masamune is secretly gathering spirit stones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/06146185d559f4843e92144dddf3147a.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=870 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/423befc80714507902ffc91a80d31ff0.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Defiant Honor<br>Fight your way through the Siege of Osaka's winter campaign as you follow the story of one of Japan's greatest generals from the Warring States period, the brave Sanada Yukimura.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/4e2f1dd396258b4919d3a4292da215ea.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=870 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/4865dfa8ff45be165b8a6cd16182de6b.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Bloodshed's End<br>Join the summer campaign of the Siege of Osaka as the Warring States period draws to a close in this, the final chapter of William's tale.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/61e8d8839654d874bffe8abc6357d109.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=870 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/139adf53509f5d3509771808085c3294.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Steam Exclusive Bonus<br>Enjoy wearing the \"Dharmachakra Kabuto,\" a helmet exclusive to the Steam version of Nioh! You can claim yours by selecting \"Boons\" from a shrine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/4ef987d2167bb8541bfe0395427cbee4.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=616 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Ready to die? Experience the newest brutal action game from Team NINJA and Koei Tecmo Games. In the age of samurai, a lone traveler lands on the shores of Japan. He must fight his way through the vicious warriors and supernatural Yokai that infest the land in order to find that which he seeks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/ab0961e37bba777ec859c3e8368c1e33.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/7c4edb97087cb46b1fb839a98daaf956.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br> The Complete Edition contains the full game, as well as the three expansions with additional story chapters: Dragon of the North, Defiant Honor, and Bloodshed's End.<br><br>Dragon of the North<br>This expansion opens up the Tohoku region, where the \"one-eyed dragon\" Date Masamune is secretly gathering spirit stones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/06146185d559f4843e92144dddf3147a.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=870 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/423befc80714507902ffc91a80d31ff0.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Defiant Honor<br>Fight your way through the Siege of Osaka's winter campaign as you follow the story of one of Japan's greatest generals from the Warring States period, the brave Sanada Yukimura.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/4e2f1dd396258b4919d3a4292da215ea.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=870 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/4865dfa8ff45be165b8a6cd16182de6b.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Bloodshed's End<br>Join the summer campaign of the Siege of Osaka as the Warring States period draws to a close in this, the final chapter of William's tale.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/61e8d8839654d874bffe8abc6357d109.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=870 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/139adf53509f5d3509771808085c3294.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Steam Exclusive Bonus<br>Enjoy wearing the \"Dharmachakra Kabuto,\" a helmet exclusive to the Steam version of Nioh! You can claim yours by selecting \"Boons\" from a shrine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/4ef987d2167bb8541bfe0395427cbee4.avif?t=1760595804\" width=616 height=616 /></span>",
